The paper deals with image captioning, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a sequence-to-sequence model using recurrent neural networks (RNN), which falls under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with multimodal translation, which involves both visual and textual modalities, making cs.MM (Multimedia) a likely sub-category as well.
